<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.1.8">
<l>iruḷiṉ ṟiṇivaṇṇa mānīrk kaḻiyēpōy</l>
<l>maruḷuṟ ṟirāppaka ṟuñcilunī tuñcāyā</l>
<l>luruḷuñ cakaṭa mutaitta perumāṉā</l>
<l>raruḷiṉ perunacaiyā lāḻāntu nontāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Backwater with dark water the colour of solid darkness, going,</l>
<l>even if, being in confusion, day [and] night sleep you don’t sleep.</l>
<l>You suffer, overwhelmed by great longing for the grace</l>
<l>of the great lord who kicked the rolling cart.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
